{"tid":2251251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事，長文慎入)我嗰兩個朋友點樣7日內俾騙徒呃咗三千幾蚊","createTime":"2020-10-20T16:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T12:40:22.000Z","uid":11043,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac0583b6d96bcfc6573bf7828b7610ff7391a82","tid":2251251,"uid":11043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"代朋友post <br />\n<br />\n事源係咁，我地兩個fd係旺角返pt，有間店叫'煮家男'自稱無味精，可以$500 26餐當一個月咁計，雖然唔算損失好多，但佢地的確係慣犯同集團式經營，呃完呢瓣就再呃其他瓣數。<br />\n<br />\n入數紙紀錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DdUumz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DdUumz.jpg&h=bc326941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JvfYeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JvfYeG.jpg&h=e70e3c65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEbVYeH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEbVYeH.jpg&h=06720fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tF3673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tF3673.jpg&h=4aafbce4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7O6ZFtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7O6ZFtd.jpg&h=0a174309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對話圖:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSusPnt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSusPnt.jpg&h=676d168f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bK09nu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bK09nu.jpg&h=2ef2b59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hn8k9nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhn8k9nv.jpg&h=1587c97c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eXVdP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eXVdP0.jpg&h=5b020a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(由於限住十幅圖係個post,所以post左少少先)<br />\n<br />\n我個兩個fd本身岩岩失業先搵到份pt做下，真係好窮，見佢咁平就買咗。<br />\n但係呢班騙子可能見佢地好呃，就係咁比我嗰兩個fd discount，r佢哋買多啲，一r就比佢哋呃咗3000幾，差唔多係佢地13日人工！<br />\n<br />\n點知買呢就話有182餐，送咗13餐之後，就成日借啲意唔送！<br />\n啱啱開頭就話舖頭被爆竊，過幾日就水浸，要停幾日咁，停停下，一停停咗兩個星期！<br />\n<br />\n佢哋覺得唔對路就要求佢退款，佢就索性影都唔見埋，原本話10月3號前覆，依家已經失聯，所有野已讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n我哋試用其他電話搵佢，佢就連fb page都del埋，本身店舖tel num（6字頭）已經完全失聯，但入數tel num仲有人用緊（8字頭）。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋兩個都曾經搵8字頭number，打電話一係唔聽，一係就cut線，whatsapp不讀不回。<br />\n<br />\n報警都報左2次，popo話呢排好忙，叫我地自己釣到佢再打999<br />\n去銀行申請錯誤匯款，銀行就話會全面配合警方行動，除此之外最多就係幫我哋打電話叫佢還錢，完全陷入左死胡同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoWOyOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoWOyOO.jpg&h=290cf22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有佢任何消息或資料，希望大家可以幫手提供<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家淨係知道騙子叫做Varro Chan(全名Chan Chixx nax Varro，x係唔知既字母)，泰國人，自稱兒童行為治療師，另外有做托兒服務，我哋用佢個名喺其他平台度搵到佢其他嘅Account，例如Carousell 旋轉拍賣發現騙徒蹤跡。<br />\n<br />\n騙徒資料:<br />\n疑似12年畢業於何文田新法書院(或者係新法度做野)<br />\n<br />\nFB名:Varro Chan <br />\nFB Link:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverhonyt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilverhonyt&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=f02f3cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silverhonyt</a><br />\n<br />\nIg名:varrochan<br />\nig link:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/varrochan?igshid=1ejodcy7djje9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fvarrochan%3Figshid%3D1ejodcy7djje9&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e87b4701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/varrochan?igshid=1ejodcy7djje9</a><br />\n<br />\nCarousell :<a href=\"https://carousell.com/chanvarro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcarousell.com%2Fchanvarro&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1b2fe091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://carousell.com/chanvarro</a><br />\n<br />\n電話:84814127 / 68182678<br />\n<br />\n另外騙徒Varro Chan(同名同姓)仲疑似涉及6年前既虐狗案，又係冇捉到，又完全冇後續處理，依家佢又繼續分別以無牌餐廳同無牌托兒中心呃其他人。<br />\n<br />\n虐狗事件link:<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20140530/NBAZYM5JLWZBKUJYJOGVXYSJ34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20140530%2FNBAZYM5JLWZBKUJYJOGVXYSJ34%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6319fc10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20140530%2FNBAZYM5JLWZBKUJYJOGVXYSJ34%2F&h=a729de9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20140530/NBAZYM5JLWZBKUJYJOGVXYSJ34/</a><br />\n<br />\n託兒事件post:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=4479044855501537&amp;set=gm.2453463988279818&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D4479044855501537%26set%3Dgm.2453463988279818%26type%3D3&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=d369c0b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=4479044855501537&amp;set=gm.2453463988279818&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n有個員工自稱受雇於佢，幫佢喺Facebook po文呃人,叫Jerry Li（全名Li Ka Hei)<br />\n之前讀天主教普照中學<br />\nFB名:Jerry Li<br />\nFB Link:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jerrylikahei\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjerrylikahei&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=5e603603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jerrylikahei</a>"},{"pid":"523194642526694fc44aa4a5f1daaf806fbdbe10","tid":2251251,"uid":11043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"騙徒1 Varro Chan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNtdKY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNtdKY2.jpg&h=ed91f321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7q37co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7q37co.jpg&h=e5525977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ug7RwD